                <li>Access tokens: until you disconnect your account or they expire</li>
                <li>Published content records (error logs): up to 90 days</li>
                <li>Analytics data: up to 12 months</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>17. Data Security</h4>
            <p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal data, including encrypted storage of access tokens and secure HTTPS transmission.</p>

            <h4>18. Automated Decision-Making</h4>
            <p>As a responsible company, we do not use automatic decision-making or profiling that produces legal or similarly significant effects.</p>

            <h4>19. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h4>
